---
// Assets
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import HeroImage from "@/images/assets/heroImage.png";
// Fundations
import Text from "@/components/fundations/elements/Text.astro";
import Kicker from "@/components/fundations/elements/Kicker.astro";
import Button from "@/components/fundations/elements/Button.astro";
import Wrapper from "@/components/fundations/containers/Wrapper.astro";
---

<section>
  <Wrapper variant="standard" class="pt-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div>
        <Kicker variant="default">Mulberry Accounting</Kicker>
        <Text
          tag="h1"
          variant="displayLG"
          class="text-base-900 text-balance font-medium tracking-tight mt-8 font-display"
        >
Most consultants focus on 30% (tech).<br/> <br/>We specialize in 70% (people)        </Text>
      </div>
      <div>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-600 lg:text-balance">
BCG's research shows AI transformation is 10% algorithms, 20% data and technology, 70% people and culture. Most consultants focus on the 30%. We specialize in the 70%.
Insight Statement (Not Problem Statement)
The failure mode in AI adoption is predictable: organizations invest in technically sound solutions that never scale beyond pilot users. The constraint isn't capability—it's readiness.
Our thesis: Adoption rates are deterministic, not random. Cultural readiness, change management capability, and trust infrastructure predict outcomes more reliably than model accuracy or system performance.
Our methodology: We assess readiness before you invest, build capability systematically, and adjust financial projections for adoption realit
    </Text>
        <Button
          variant="muted"
          size="base"
          isLink={true}
          href="/system/overview"
          class="mt-8 w-fit"
        >
          See all pages
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Wrapper>
  <Wrapper variant="paddingLess" class="pt-12">
    <Image
      src={HeroImage}
      alt="Hero Image"
      width={1200}
      height={1400}
      loading="eager"
      decoding="async"
      class="w-full max-h-200 object-cover object-top"
    />
  </Wrapper>
</section>
